Package: jnctex
Title: JNC LaTeX Template for Academic Manuscripts
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Joseph N.", "Cohen", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joseph.cohen@qc.cuny.edu")
Description: Pandoc/Quarto LaTeX template for academic manuscripts in
    sociology and related fields. Provides font presets for different
    journal registers (humanities, demography, methods), anonymization
    support, line numbering, and two-column layout. Use jnc_use() to
    install the template bundle into a new project directory.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
